function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idActorNPC)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idClone) then
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idClone)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, npc_Edan_Post, "npc_walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idClone, animset_Routine_Farmer)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idClone)
	end
end
